
On startup:

- Print startup text at the top
- Player starts as dealer


Playing the hand:

- clear screen

- on every draw, draw:
    . remaining player and AI hands
    . desired message at the top of the window
    . current list of played cards (cleared after we pass 31)
    . current AI and player scores



    . AI and player hands take up the left side of the screen
    . played card list can go in the row between AI and player hands
    . scores go to the right of each hand

- on ai or player turn:
    . find a valid card to play
    . play it (add to played card stack)
    . score any points obtained
    . update announcement message
    . redraw board
